Interface JdbcDataMapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataMapper, Documentable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JdbcDataMapperImpl

    public interface JdbcDataMapper
extends DataMapper
    A representation of the model object 'Jdbc Data Mapper'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Jdbc Driver
    • Sql
    • Properties
